text: Boguszyn may refer to the following places in Poland: *Boguszyn, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Boguszyn, West Pomeranian Voivodeship (north-west Poland) *Boguszyn, Leszno County in Greater Poland Voivodeship (west-central Poland) *Boguszyn, Środa Wielkopolska County in Greater Poland Voivodeship (west-central Poland)
title: Boguszyn
